    "asOf": "2021-01-21",
    "date": "2021-05-17T18:16:53Z",
    "text": "Vaccinate More Americans Act of 2021\n\nThis bill allows health care providers to disregard federal, state, or local laws or guidelines that prioritize COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) vaccinations for essential workers and other at-risk groups when necessary to prevent the expiration of a vaccine dose.\n\nIf a dose cannot be administered to a member of a prioritized group before it expires, a provider may vaccinate an individual in a lower priority group."
  },
